OPTO TECH CORP said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 11.92% to NT$542,748,000 from NT$616,202,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            542,748          616,202    
YOY%             -11.92%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,093,631        2,481,188   
YOY%             -15.62% 
=================================================================
 